title: Bellator Fight Master 01
description:
Fight Master: Bellator MMA is a mixed martial arts based reality television series. It centers around the promotion Bellator Fighting Championships and airs on Spike TV. The series debuted on June 19, 2013.

The series was officially announced by Bellator and Spike TV at a press conference on February 5, 2013. The coaches and trainers for the series, which will feature 32 welterweight fighters, will be Randy Couture, Frank Shamrock, Greg Jackson, and Joe Warren. The 32 fighters will be competing for a spot in Bellator's welterweight tournament. The weekly series will culminate in a live season finale on Spike TV with the winner advancing into the fall welterweight tournament.
